{
  &quot;prompt&quot;: &quot;A floor plan redesign for a small rectangular bedroom with a bed, desk, dresser, nightstand, and a bathroom. The new layout should optimize the room for mental clarity, rest, and emotional stability. The bed is now anchored against the left wall with the nightstand beside it. The desk is placed under a window for natural light. The dresser is moved to a wall with space to access the closet easily. The cluttered corner near the bathroom is cleared. The overall space feels open, peaceful, and intentional. Clean lines, soft lighting, and natural flow.&quot;,
  &quot;size&quot;: &quot;1024x1024&quot;
}

{
  &quot;prompt&quot;: &quot;A realistic top-down floor plan layout of a small bedroom. The room has a bed anchored to the left wall, with a nightstand beside it. There&#x27;s a desk under a window on the top wall. The closet is on the bottom right wall, with a dresser placed nearby. The bathroom door is on the top right corner wall, and the main room door is directly in front of the bathroom door, on the opposite (bottom left) wall. A small table and chair are removed from the cluttered bathroom corner. The floor is a mix of wood and black-and-white tile. The layout feels clearer, open, and energetically balanced for calm and focus.&quot;,
  &quot;size&quot;: &quot;1024x1024&quot;
}

{
  &quot;prompt&quot;: &quot;A clean and minimal bedroom floor plan layout optimized for stability and clarity. The room has a bed anchored to a solid wall (not floating), a desk positioned under a window, a dresser with clear walking space, a nightstand within easy reach from the bed, and a clutter-free open corner near the bathroom. The room door is directly in front of the bathroom door. Include calming layout flow with practical spacing.&quot;,
  &quot;size&quot;: &quot;1024x1024&quot;
}

{
  &quot;prompt&quot;: &quot;A cloudy sky with eerie, natural cloud formations that resemble a hunched, shadowy humanoid figure with a bowed head and arms tucked in, positioned just right of a vertical wooden utility pole. The sky is overcast and moody, with trees and power lines below, giving a mysterious atmosphere. The figure should look like it&#x27;s part of the clouds but subtly distinguishable, as if watching quietly.&quot;,
  &quot;size&quot;: &quot;1024x1024&quot;
}
